What is the government doing about it?

454
00:31:01,069 --> 00:31:04,572
Do they even know what's going on?

455
00:31:05,907 --> 00:31:07,659
Mr. Ramos!

456
00:31:08,034 --> 00:31:09,828
You may not be aware of it

457
00:31:10,995 --> 00:31:12,664
but in Singapore

458
00:31:12,706 --> 00:31:15,250
migrant domestic workers

459
00:31:15,291 --> 00:31:17,585
