460
00:31:17,627 --> 00:31:21,297
There's also a process for abused women.

461
00:31:21,631 --> 00:31:24,134
So they they can also be helped...

462
00:31:27,303 --> 00:31:28,930
Do you realize Johnny...

463
00:31:29,639 --> 00:31:33,268
Some men treat their penis like a gun?

464
00:31:34,352 --> 00:31:35,729
No, really!

465
00:31:36,354 --> 00:31:39,315
Because when they are mad at women...

466
00:31:39,649 --> 00:31:42,193
