467
00:31:42,777 --> 00:31:43,862
Aren't I right?

468
00:31:45,947 --> 00:31:47,282
Have you seen...

469
00:31:47,323 --> 00:31:50,702
Did you watch the film, Full Metal Jacket?

470
00:31:51,036 --> 00:31:52,454
There's a scene there where

471
00:31:53,038 --> 00:31:55,790
