472
00:31:55,874 --> 00:31:57,667
And their chant goes like this:

473
00:31:58,043 --> 00:31:59,711
This is my weapon.

474
00:31:59,753 --> 00:32:01,338
This is my gun.

475
00:32:01,379 --> 00:32:03,006
This is for business.

476
00:32:03,048 --> 00:32:04,758
This is for fun!

477
00:32:06,426 --> 00:32:09,095
You mean, they hold their thing...

478
00:32:09,137 --> 00:32:10,180
Like this?

479
00:32:14,267 --> 00:32:15,352
You know what?

480
00:32:15,393 --> 00:32:17,228
I know this guy.

481
00:32:17,270 --> 00:32:19,898
It's not a gun he likens his penis to.

482
00:32:19,939 --> 00:32:21,149
Gold!

483
00:32:21,483 --> 00:32:22,359
Who?

484
00:32:22,942 --> 00:32:24,402
My ex-husband.

485
00:32:25,236 --> 00:32:26,279
Back then...

486
00:32:27,322 --> 00:32:28,907
Everytime he was mad at me,

487
00:32:28,948 --> 00:32:30,784
