493
00:32:46,591 --> 00:32:48,259
Then why are you still thinking about him?

494
00:32:52,972 --> 00:32:54,974
That gold was precious.

495
00:33:05,985 --> 00:33:07,112
Lea.

496
00:33:07,153 --> 00:33:10,073
Sister, this is my daughter.

497
00:33:10,115 --> 00:33:12,242
This is Maya? She's so pretty!

498
00:33:12,283 --> 00:33:14,285
- How are you?
- Fine, sister.

499
00:33:14,619 --> 00:33:16,287
And smart, too!

500
00:33:16,329 --> 00:33:19,874
That woman who kept
calling us and crying is here.

501
00:33:19,916 --> 00:33:23,086
Goodness! She's the wife of Sigmund Olivares.

502
00:33:23,128 --> 00:33:25,130
Does his name ring a bell?

503
00:33:25,296 --> 00:33:26,548
Sportsman?

504
00:33:26,589 --> 00:33:27,465
Correct!

505
00:33:27,507 --> 00:33:31,469
Sportsman, promoter, banker
and I don't know what else.

506
00:33:31,511 --> 00:33:34,264
If you saw her, your heart will break.

507
00:33:34,305 --> 00:33:36,558
She's severely battered and almost hysterical.

508
00:33:36,599 --> 00:33:39,519
Now all she wants is never
to see the husband again.

509
00:33:39,561 --> 00:33:42,939
I don't ever wanna see your face again.
You understand?

510
00:33:42,981 --> 00:33:45,567
I'm leaving you for good Sigmund!

511
00:33:46,609 --> 00:33:49,738
I'm here at the Women Crisis
and Survival Center now.

512
00:33:50,363 --> 00:33:52,282
What is the address of this center?

513
00:33:52,323 --> 00:33:55,410
I'm telling this bastard that
I don't want to ever go back to him.

514
00:33:55,452 --> 00:33:58,621
Well not unless of course you still
wanna make a go of this marriage.

515
00:33:58,663 --> 00:34:00,665
Stop it! You're going to fall.

516
00:34:01,082 --> 00:34:03,668
Stop being so stubborn!

517
00:34:05,378 --> 00:34:06,087
Stop it!

518
00:34:06,171 --> 00:34:09,299
Maya, here it is! Give me just a minute!

519
00:34:09,341 --> 00:34:10,050
I don't want to!

520
00:34:10,508 --> 00:34:11,009
I don't want to!

521
00:34:11,051 --> 00:34:13,428
