923
01:01:10,503 --> 01:01:14,799
The love of a man for a woman
or a woman for a man.

924
01:01:16,176 --> 01:01:18,053
The one that comes with sex and lust.

925
01:01:18,094 --> 01:01:19,721
Jesus, Mary, and Joseph!

926
01:01:19,763 --> 01:01:23,016
You see, even if you're a nun,
you're still a human being.

927
01:01:23,391 --> 01:01:26,311
Priests are also human beings.

928
01:01:28,271 --> 01:01:30,815
Look at Father Ignacio.

929
01:01:31,232 --> 01:01:32,776
Doesn't he have a mistress?

930
01:01:32,817 --> 01:01:34,527
