957
01:03:01,948 --> 01:03:02,949
Let's shop!

958
01:03:03,033 --> 01:03:04,325
We're going to buy a broom.

959
01:03:04,701 --> 01:03:06,578
Let's visit the Grotto first.

960
01:03:06,619 --> 01:03:08,538
The Grotto again?

961
01:03:10,957 --> 01:03:14,044
After the Grotto, then we buy your broom...

962
01:03:39,778 --> 01:03:41,488
