he'll become a handsome baby.

1012
01:05:57,832 --> 01:05:59,793
Mom, is he also my brother?

1013
01:05:59,834 --> 01:06:00,627
Of course not!

1014
01:06:00,669 --> 01:06:03,213
But he can be if you want.

1015
01:06:03,463 --> 01:06:06,591
