Press this.

1027
01:07:17,996 --> 01:07:19,164
It's working!

1028
01:07:19,205 --> 01:07:19,873
Really?

1029
01:07:19,914 --> 01:07:20,457
Yes!

1030
01:07:40,477 --> 01:07:41,686
Hi!

1031
01:07:44,022 --> 01:07:45,357
Wow!

1032
01:07:47,067 --> 01:07:49,069
Thank you, Maya!

1033
01:07:52,572 --> 01:07:53,948
Isn't he handsome?

1034
01:07:59,329 --> 01:08:00,622
Thank you...

1035
01:08:01,748 --> 01:08:03,416
