1040
01:08:16,596 --> 01:08:17,847
Time for milk!

1041
01:08:17,889 --> 01:08:19,683
Yes, it's time for milk now!

1042
01:08:19,724 --> 01:08:21,893
Okay, time for milk!

1043
01:08:21,935 --> 01:08:23,353
