1064
01:09:38,053 --> 01:09:40,972
After giving priority
to your job over your children.

1065
01:09:42,140 --> 01:09:43,224
I'll just be outside.

1066
01:09:50,190 --> 01:09:52,150
You know, you're just perfect.

1067
01:09:52,442 --> 01:09:54,277
Even in front of other people!

1068
01:09:54,319 --> 01:09:55,445
